title: Third Age: Divide & Conquer - Isengard #15 - Diplomatic Issues
description:
Welcome back to the Isengard Campaign.  The wrath of the white wizard is unstoppable.  Our relations are not getting any better with Mordor.  War could be around the corner, but not just yet...enjoy :D
